{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e4aa9d77d1","title":"首都红卫兵纠察队队员六项守则","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c92cfd35fa","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":25,"articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"89d86a8bd3","name":"《首都红卫兵纠察队》西城指挥部"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c0c914f939","type":"title","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队队员六项守则","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"853cff6cb1","type":"paragraph","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队队员六项守则","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a2f9d8a90","type":"paragraph","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队西城分队指挥部","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8234dd088c","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.08.25","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8580e48d6","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 坚决按照毛主席的指示办事。努力学习最高指示，忠实执行最高指示，热情宣传最高指示，勇敢捍卫最高指示。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d305a6c658","type":"paragraph","text":"坚决按十六条精神办事。学习十六条，熟悉十六条，掌握十六条，运用十六条。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6a0e9c4df","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 大学解放军，大力发扬“三八作风”，雷厉风行，坚决做到：召之即来，来之能战，战之能胜。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c228f0992c","type":"paragraph","text":"三、 必须坚决贯彻“三大纪律八项注意”。严禁打人及变相体罚，严禁侮辱人。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"830d7a359f","type":"paragraph","text":"四、 谦虚、谨慎、戒骄戒躁、全心全意为人民服务，做人民忠实的勤务员。坚决防止特殊化。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03be1ff2ae","type":"paragraph","text":"五、 只有值勤时戴臂章，不值勤时一律不准戴臂章，臂章由班长掌握。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ec85478aa","type":"paragraph","text":"六、 一定要注意深入调查研究，在任何情况下，都要沉着、冷静，严防阶级敌人乘机捣乱破坏。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2bb6cf6854","type":"paragraph","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e34fa464a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（发表于首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部：《首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部通令集（1-10）》）","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e4aa9d77d1","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}